textAnnotations.description:
"YOU HAVEN'T CONTRBUTED
TO ANY REPUBLICAN
CAMPAIGNS, ALL YOUR
FRIENDS ARE DEMOCRATS E MIGHT WANT
AND YOURE NOT
FROM TEXAS!
ID SAY YOU'RE
OFF THE LIST...
The Bush administration
seeks to revise prolisions
of the Endangered Species
Act to bring it into line
with the way the rest of
government run :
BESIDES
TO SERVE YOU ATA
DINNER."
